abilities.name: Quick make Camp Fire Kit
abilities.tooltip:
Pick up the following materials in the correct order or click on this once they're in your inventory to get a Camp Fire Kit. A handy dandy kit for starting a fire, can be used to cook meat, heat yourself up or burn buildings, might burn your own buildings too :

1x |cff1FBF00Tinder|r + 1x |cffFF0202Flint|r + 1x |cff1FBF00Stick|r

If you do not have enough inventory to craft to pick all items, you can use the craft master 5000 at the center of the map. This Quick Make ability will find the nearest material and craft the said building, material have to be either on the ground just next to the unit or inside its inventory. For more information abouts item, type |cffFFD700-recipes|r, all the items are listed there.

If you do not have enough inventory to craft to pick all items, you can use the craft master 5000 at the center of the map. This Quick Make ability will find the nearest material and craft the said building, material have to be either on the ground just next to the unit or inside its inventory. For more information abouts item, type |cffFFD700-recipes|r, all the items are listed there.
